  <h2>Leadership Workflow (ordered)</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Define strategic goals</li>
    <li>Coordinate cross-disciplinary teams</li>
    <li>Implement patient-centered initiatives</li>
    <li>Review metrics & refine</li>
  </ol>

